name: Forest series Black&White: This is where the mushrooms grow 02
description:
Taavi Varm (2021) | 2160 × 2160 jpg | www.varmstudio.com

Forest is something sacred, and I try to capture the mystical atmosphere of these remote wild places. It feels like the time has stopped when the photo has no colors, and I could not ever go back there.
The exact location of this spot is in northern Estonia close to the Baltic Sea at coordinates: 59°28'53.8"N 25°41'01.0"E
